Q_str.description: The python code that creates the Q matrix (quadratic objective function).

c_str.description: The python code that creates the c vector (linear objective function).

A_str.description: The python code that creates the A matrix (matrix of inequality constraints).

b_str.description: The python code that creates the b vector (vector of inequality constraints).

Aeq_str.description: The python code that creates the Aeq matrix (matrix of equality constraints).

beq_str.description: The python code that creates the beq vector (vector of equality constraints).

lb_str.description: The python code that creates the lb scalar (lower bound).

ub_str.description: The python code that creates the ub scalar (upper bound).
